FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777187148
OL,3,CITV's new drama Secret Service 'peaks
OL,4,Cbehind curtain' of spying and politics
OL,6,FI don't imagine it's all jet-setting,
OL,7,Fsupercar-driving and bad guy-battling.
OL,8,FThat being said, even as an adult, I
OL,9,Fstill allow myself to ponder the
OL,10,Fpossibility of the luxurious life of
OL,11,Fespionage.
OL,13,FITV's new drama Secret Service blends
OL,14,Fa career in intelligence with the
OL,15,Frealities of human existence.
OL,17,FIt stars Gemma Arterton - who already
OL,18,Fboasts the James Bond franchise on her
OL,19,FCV - as Kate Henderson, a senior MI6
OL,20,Foperative.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777187148
OL,3,CITV's new drama Secret Service 'peaks
OL,4,Cbehind curtain' of spying and politics
OL,6,FI sat down with the actress on set in
OL,7,FMalta, back when the series was
OL,8,Ffilming in April 2025.
OL,10,FPerched on the pews of a church (it'll
OL,11,Fmake sense when you watch the first
OL,12,Fepisode), Arterton says she was 'quite
OL,13,Famazed that they thought I was capable
OL,14,Fof playing someone' like Kate.
OL,16,F"There has been lots of talk about a
OL,17,Ffemale Bond and it's not like that.
OL,18,FWhat sets this apart from a lot of
OL,19,Fothers is that it looks at the
OL,20,Fdomestic as well.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777187148
OL,3,CITV's new drama Secret Service 'peaks
OL,4,Cbehind curtain' of spying and politics
OL,6,F"She is a mother of two teenagers, she
OL,7,Fhas a busy life, how do you live a
OL,8,Flife with so much secrecy? It's hard
OL,9,Fenough being a parent, without all
OL,10,Fthis other stuff on top. I really
OL,11,Fconnected with that actually."
OL,13,FEvery year, TV channels and streamers
OL,14,Fback projects within the espionage
OL,15,Fgenre. There is a bankability about
OL,16,Fthem which stems from an initiate
OL,17,Fintrigue from viewers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777187148
OL,3,CITV's new drama Secret Service 'peaks
OL,4,Cbehind curtain' of spying and politics
OL,6,F"I think it's that we don't get to see
OL,7,Fit in real life', Gemma says. "The
OL,8,Fworld of it, when you fictionalise it,
OL,9,Fis so enticing. People enjoy watching
OL,10,Fanything that is clandestine or
OL,11,Fforbidden. It's an endlessly fruitful
OL,12,Fgenre."
OL,14,FAttempting to divulge as few spoilers
OL,15,Fas possible, I will tell you that
OL,16,FSecret Service is centred around Kate
OL,17,FHenderson learning that a senior
OL,18,FBritish politician could be a
OL,19,Fpotential Russian asset.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777187148
OL,3,CITV's new drama Secret Service 'peaks
OL,4,Cbehind curtain' of spying and politics
OL,6,FThe storyline is based on a book by
OL,7,Fthe same name, written by ITV News
OL,8,Fpresenter Tom Bradby.
OL,10,F"We're here in Malta, it's very
OL,11,Fexotic", Bradby notes. "They are
OL,12,Fwatching quite an exotic spy thriller,
OL,13,Fbut we really wanted the audience to
OL,14,Ffeel like this is a peak behind the
OL,15,Fcurtain for how real life could be.
OL,16,FReal life spying, real life politics.
OL,18,F"I grew up on the books of the old
OL,19,FCold War and I'd like to think this is
OL,20,Fthe first proper drama of the new Cold
OL,21,FWar."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777187148
OL,3,CITV's new drama Secret Service 'peaks
OL,4,Cbehind curtain' of spying and politics
OL,6,FThe show has something of a heavy-
OL,7,Fhitting cast. In addition to Gemma
OL,8,FArterton, you've got the likes of Rafe
OL,9,FSpall, Mark Stanley, Alex Kingston,
OL,10,FRoger Allam and Khalid Abdalla.
OL,12,FThere's a big name behind the camera
OL,13,Ftoo. Oscar-winning film director James
OL,14,FMarsh is overseeing the first 3 of 5
OL,15,Ftotal episodes.
OL,17,FIn recent years, the entertainment
OL,18,Findustry's once hard lines between
OL,19,Ffilm and TV have massively blurred.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777187148
OL,3,CITV's new drama Secret Service 'peaks
OL,4,Cbehind curtain' of spying and politics
OL,6,FMarsh believes that "you are trying to
OL,7,Fbring a sense of cinema to television
OL,8,Fand I think you can".
OL,10,F"People now mostly have quite good
OL,11,Ftelevisions, so the work you do is
OL,12,Factually quite translatable from
OL,13,Fcinema to TV and there is no snobbery
OL,14,Ffor me. They are both great mediums
OL,15,Ffor storytelling.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777187148
OL,3,CITV's new drama Secret Service 'peaks
OL,4,Cbehind curtain' of spying and politics
OL,6,F"This story can now unfold in 5
OL,7,Fepisodes in a way it couldn't in a
OL,8,Ffilm, you'd compress it too much. You
OL,9,Fdon't have the space to nuance scenes
OL,10,Fand characters. I'm glad we got the
OL,11,Fbigger compass of time."
OL,13,FI might be speaking solely for myself,
OL,14,Fbut I think most people deep down
OL,15,Freckon they'd be a pretty good spy. I
OL,16,Fthink in practice, we'd all be
OL,17,Fexceptionally awful.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
