PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777187148
OL,3,CITV's new drama Secret Service 'peaks
OL,4,Cbehind curtain' of spying and politics
OL,6,FHaving seen the first two episodes of
OL,7,FSecret Service, I can tell you that
OL,8,FGemma Arterton is beyond convincing in
OL,9,Fthe role of MI6 operative.
OL,11,FHowever, she doesn't give herself any
OL,12,Fchance of doing the job well in real
OL,13,Flife.
OL,15,F"I would be an atrocious spy," she
OL,16,Flaughs. "I think the first thing that
OL,17,Fwould give me away is that I blush.
OL,18,FIt's such an involuntary reaction, you
OL,19,Fcannot blush as a spy or asset.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777187148
OL,3,CITV's new drama Secret Service 'peaks
OL,4,Cbehind curtain' of spying and politics
OL,6,F"I don't think I'm very good at
OL,7,Fkeeping things to myself. I'm private
OL,8,Fbut I'm not secretive. I'm clumsy as
OL,9,Fwell, I'm not good at being covert."
OL,11,FSecret Service starts Monday 27th
OL,12,FApril, 9pm on ITV1 and ITVX
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
